--------------------------------------------------
CCK FIELD PLUGIN FOR SEBLOD 2.0 CCK FOR JOOMLA 1.7
--------------------------------------------------

Name: SD Concat
Author: Simon Dowdles - www.onestuckpixel.com
Twitter: @simondowdles

Description

Concatenates any cck fields, plain text values & limited pre-defined variables into one value. Ideal for unique titles
	
Instructions

*Plain text to appear in square brackets like [plain text here]. Fields enclosed with # like #field_name# and predefined variables like $date, $time, $username & $userid
*All fields (cck, plain text and variables) are to be comma separated
*Field Separator determines the character used to glue all values together.
*Example: [Article crated by],$username,[on],$date,[in category ID],#art_catid# *Results in: "Article created by Simon Dowdles on 2011-08-26 in category ID 9" where I would have used NO field separator character.